Key Match Events: Mike Yastrzemski hit a game-winning home run to beat the Milwaukee Brewers
Post-Match Reflections: Following the win, San Francisco moved to 67-66 on the season, keeping themselves alive in the chase to get back into a National League Wild Card spot
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Giants opened up the game with a 1-0 lead after Lamonte Wade Jr. grounded out to second, scoring Grant McCray
Matt Chapman also hit a solo home run in the top of the fourth and McCray added his own solo homer in the top of the fifth
